{
  "page": "Pyramid of Ullhor",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b>pyramid of Ullhor</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Pyramid\" title=\"Pyramid\">pyramid</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> and is the seat of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_of_Ullhor\" title=\"House of Ullhor\">House of Ullhor</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dace_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dace with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dace with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>During the <a href=\"/index.php/Siege_of_Astapor\" title=\"Siege of Astapor\">siege of Astapor</a> by <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>, new <a href=\"/index.php/Unsullied\" title=\"Unsullied\">Unsullied</a> lead a sortie out of <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a> but are defeated by an <a href=\"/index.php/Ghiscari_legions\" title=\"Ghiscari legions\">iron legion</a> from <a href=\"/index.php/New_Ghis\" title=\"New Ghis\">New Ghis</a>. While feasting overnight in the pyramid of Ullhor, survivors from the battle <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poison</a> their <a href=\"/index.php/Wine\" title=\"Wine\">wine</a> to kill themselves.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Pyramid_of_Ullhor&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd30.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_30\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 30\">Chapter 30</a>, Daenerys V.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404083145\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.010 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 87/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8542/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 438/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 526/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    6.157      1 -total\n 70.47%    4.339      1 Template:Ref\n 41.40%    2.549      1 Template:Ref/core\n 28.02%    1.725      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:31956-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404083145 and revision id 328341\n -->\n",
